title: Alden Ehrenreich
summary: Alden Caleb Ehrenreich (; born November 22, 1989) is an American actor. He began his career by appearing in Supernatural (2005), and Francis Ford Coppola's films Tetro (2009) and Twixt (2011). Following supporting roles in the 2013 films Blue Jasmine and Stoker, he starred in the Coen brothers comedy Hail, Caesar! (2016), for which he gained praise. He went on to play Han Solo in the space Western film Solo: A Star Wars Story (2018) and starred in the dystopian television series Brave New World (2020).
